OL,3,CAnti-racism campaigners gather in
OL,4,CCardiff amid fear of far-right protest
OL,6,FAround 150 anti-racism campaigners
OL,7,Fgathered in Cardiff city centre in
OL,8,Fresponse to fears of possible far-
OL,9,Fright protests taking place.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Police said it was aware
OL,12,Fof planned events on Friday and over
OL,13,Fthe weekend but it had no reason to
OL,14,Fexpect disorder.
OL,16,FOne campaigner told ITV Cymru Wales:
OL,17,F"We are here today to counter a
OL,18,Fpotential far-right riot. There was
OL,19,Fword that there might be something
OL,20,Fgoing on.
