OL,6,FA police spokesperson had said on
OL,7,FFriday: "South Wales Police is aware
OL,8,Fof planned events in Cardiff on Friday
OL,9,Fand Saturday and in Swansea on Sunday.
OL,11,F"A policing operation will be in
OL,12,Feffect and we will be working to
OL,13,Fensure that they take place safely,
OL,14,Flawfully with minimum disruption to
OL,15,Fthe wider public.
OL,17,F"We have no reason to expect disorder
OL,18,Fbut will deal robustly with anyone who
OL,19,Fchooses to commit criminal offences
OL,20,Fsuch as violence and damage."
