OL,3,CAnti-racism campaigners gather in
OL,4,CCardiff amid fear of far-right protest
OL,6,F"It is crucial that we stand together
OL,7,Fagainst any efforts to incite division
OL,8,For hatred. Council leaders from across
OL,9,FWales have met with senior police
OL,10,Fofficials seeking reassurance in terms
OL,11,Fof taking robust action where
OL,12,Fnecessary and having sufficient
OL,13,Fresources available to respond if
OL,14,Fneeded.
OL,16,F"The WLGA is working with councils
OL,17,Facross Wales as they monitor the
OL,18,Fsituation, working with local partners
OL,19,Fto help keep our communities safe."
